Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.99,Ep_Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Excruciating}Nesnesitelný {\c&H1400A9&}{Sadness}smutek{\c} {Can}může \N{Be Cured by Other}být vyléčen jinou {\c&H1400A9&}{Anguish}bolestí
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.87,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The agent of Chaos!}Agent Chaosu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.71,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is the meaning of this?}Co tím myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.59,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait. She's on our side!}Počkej. Ona je na naší straně!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.84,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{Our side?}Naší straně?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.30,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been seduced by the Foundation.}Byla jsi svedena nadací.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri saved Kotetsu.}Yuri zachránila Kotetsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.05,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you mean?}Co tím myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:11.94,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{It's true, Tsubaki-chan. I owe Shiraki-san my life.}Je to pravda, Tsubaki. Dlužím Shiraki svůj život.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:17.31,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Since awakening after the Great\N Collapse, I started having dreams.}Od probuzení po Velkém zhroucení jsem začal mít sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.34,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Dreams of my loved ones dying.}Sny ve kterých mí blízcí umírají.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{First Kotetsu's dad, then Inuki-san.}První Kotetsův táta, potom Inuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.45,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No matter how I fought,\N I couldn't change the outcome.}Jedno jak jsem bojoval, nemohl jsem změnit výsledek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.68,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Prophetic dreams of death, huh?}Prorocké sny o smrti, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.45,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Sounds like you.}Zní to jako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Then I dreamed of Kotetsu's death.}Potom co se mi zdálo o Kotetsově smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.74,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I gave up hope. I thought it was fate.}Vzdal jsem se naděje. Myslel jsem, že to byl osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.23,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{But I'm still alive.}Ale jsem stále naživu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:46.89,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri taught me that I can change fate.}Yuri mě naučila, že mohu změnit osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.86,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not logic or sentimentality.}Není to logické nebo sentimentální.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.41,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The fact that Kotetsu's still\Nhere is all we need to know.}Fakt, že je Kotetsu naživu je vše co potřebujeme vědět.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.49,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm no longer at the mercy of fate.}Už nejsem na pospas osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.48,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Sounds good to me.}To zní dobře pro mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.87,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Isn't it your goal to destroy Tokyo?}Není tvým cílem zničit Tokio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.36,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Isn't it too late to stop?}Není příliš pozdě přestat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{AVAL's goal is the extermination\Nof the Heroic Lineage.}Cílem AVALu je vyhlazení hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:15.60,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{To do that, they caused the Great Collapse\Nand are turning people into gates.}Aby to udělali, způsobili Velké zhroucení a přeměňují lidi na brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.93,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{In order to protect the Heroic Lineage,}Za účelem ochrany hrdinské linie,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:23.53,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maldeus Church is trying to destroy Tokyo,\N the breeding ground for said gates.}Maldeuský kostel se snaží zničit Tokio, živnou půdu pro brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.38,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{There is no other way.}Není jiný způsob.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.64,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The answer's simple, then.}Potom je tedy odpověď jednoduchá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:33.16,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The Heroic Lineage simply needs\N to survive without destroying Tokyo.}Hrdinská linie prostě potřebuje přežít bez toho, aniž by zničila Tokio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:37.57,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If we survive, we can stop Chaos' plan.}Pokud přežijeme, dokážeme zastavit Chaosův plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.90,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If we work together,}Pokud budeme spolupracovat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.87,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{we should be able to overcome\Nthe Foundation's attacks.}měli bychom být schopni překonat útoky nadace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.40,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Not a bad idea.}Není to špatný nápad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.08,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Though we're enemies now...}I když jsme teď nepřátelé ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.27,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't trust them.}Nevěřím jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.09,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Shoko-san...}Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.53,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The destruction of Tokyo or\N the death of the Heroic Lineage.}Zničení Tokia nebo smrt hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.65,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It can only be one of the two.}Může to být jen jeden ze dvou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:04.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri had no choice but to fight,\N but she joined us instead.}Yuri neměla na výběr bojovat, ale připojila se k nám.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.22,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotetsu was meant to die, but he was saved.}Kotetsu měl zemřít, ale byl zachráněn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Fate is already beginning to change.}Osud se opravdu začíná měnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:13.35,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been misled by your love affair.\N For you to lecture us about fate}Byli jste uvedeni v omyl vaší milostnou aférkou. Pro vás přednáška o našem osudu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.06,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{is the pinnacle of audacity.}je vrcholem drzosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I just don't want anyone else to die!}Jen nechci, aby kdokoli zemřel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Help me. Please!}Pomoz mi. Prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.57,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You already know my answer.}Mou odpověď už znáš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.56,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe I'll side with Kotecchan, then.}Možná budu na straně Kotíka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.82,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Akira?}Akiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.54,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Sure, if it means getting Haru back.}Jistě, pokud to znamená dostat Harua zpět.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.91,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll fight with you, too.}Taky s tebou budu bojovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.92,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{Do what you want.}Dělej si co chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:45.06,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{We will fulfill our duty as\N members of the Guardian State.}Budeme plnit svou povinnost jako členi strážného státu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.76,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{We don't require the help of sinners.}Nepotřebujeme pomoc hříšníků.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.01,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't.}Nepotřebují.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.96,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If you get involved, he'll dream of you next.}Pokud se připojíš, bude další sen o tobě.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.43,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll help.}Pomohu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.39,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You trust them?}Věříš jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.74,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{I want to.}Chci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.99,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Where is Yuri?!}Kde je Yuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.10,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe she betrayed us.}Možná nás zradila.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.17,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Jun, have you not heard anything?}June, neslyšel jsi něco?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.25,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Nothing.}Nic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:30.63,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{My daughter is a fool,\N but Yuri is still useful to us.}Má dcera je blázen, ale Yuri je stále užitečná pro nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.84,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Find her.}Najděte ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.86,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{How could you ignore my goodwill?}Jak jsi mohl ignorovat mou dobrou vůli?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.78,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Get involved and die, huh?}Připoj se nebo zemři, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.89,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{It'll take more than a million\N funerals to kill you.}Bude to trvat víc než milión pohřbů, aby tě zabili.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.90,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm a tough man to kill.}Je obtížné mě zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:53.37,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{If it lets me change the present,\N I'd even work with the god of death.}Pokud mě to nechá změnit současnost, pracovala bych i s bohem smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.97,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no guarantee it'll improve things.}Neexistuje žádná záruka, že se to zlepší.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.59,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{The future is based on the past.}Budoucnost je založena na minulosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.79,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If his hands are stained with blood,}Pokud jsou jeho ruce zbarveny krví,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.00,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{the future he creates will\N surely be bloodstained, too.}budoucnost, kterou vytváří, bude určitě také krvavá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.75,Shinsou main,KAIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He killed his own father so he'd survive.}Zabil vlastního otce, aby přežil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.58,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you sure?}Jsi si jistý?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:14.43,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.64,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Come with me.}Pojď se mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.25,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry. Were you waiting long?}Promiň. Čekal jsi dlouho?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.16,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No.}Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.45,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It smells good.}To voní pěkně.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.87,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm pretty confident this time.}Jsem si dost jistá tentokrát.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.81,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{These are the reports from\N the investigation 13 years ago.}Jsou to zprávy z vyšetřování před 13 lety.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:50.68,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{When I learned Kamina Chihiro\N was a vessel of Heroic Blood,}Když jsem se dozvěděl, že Kamina Chihiro byl nádobou hrdinské krve,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.33,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{I acquired them immediately.}Okamžitě jsem je získala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.50,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{The autopsy report, crime scene photos...}Pitevní zpráva, fotky z místa činu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.83,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Some of this info \Nwas never made public.}Některé z těchto informací nebyly nikdy zveřejněny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:03.31,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{What you believed to be the\Ntruth may not actually be true.}To, co jste považovali za pravdu, nemusí být pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.16,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're saying he}Říkáte tedy, {\i1}{didn't kill him?}že ho nezabil?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.90,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{13 years ago, in a neighborhood of\N summer homes in Chichibusanchu,}Před 13 lety, v sousedství letních domů v Chichibusanchu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.86,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{a family forced into a double\N suicide was discovered.}byla objevena rodina donucená k dvojí sebevraždě.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.07,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Their seven-year-old son was \Nrescued in a weakened state,}Jejich sedmiletý syn byl zachráněn v oslabeném stavu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.63,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{but the father had been dead for two weeks.}ale otec byl po dva týdny mrtvý.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:27.08,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{It's likely the son spent\N all that time with the body.}Je pravděpodobné, že syn trávil celou dobu s tělem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I... My dad...}Já... mého otce...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I killed my dad.}Zabil jsem mého otce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.40,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{He fell into a coma, and when he awoke,}Upadl do bezvědomí, a když se probudil,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.56,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{he'd lost his memories of the incident.}ztratil své vzpomínky na incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.16,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina clearly said to the cops\Nwho arrived at the scene}Kamina jasně řekl policistům, kteří přišli na místo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.36,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{that he'd killed his father!}že zabil svého otce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.64,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{He must've been confused.}Musel být zmatený.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.96,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah. That's what you cops thought,}Jo. To je to, co policajti mysleli,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.62,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{and it was treated as a forced double suicide.}a bylo považováno za nucenou dvojitou sebevraždu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:06.29,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{There were signs on Kamina Chihiro's\Nthroat that indicated he'd been choked.}Na Kamina Chihirově krku se objevily známky, které naznačovaly, že byl udušený.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.73,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{His father tried to strangle him}Jeho otec se ho snažil uškrtit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.05,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{but changed his mind and \Nstabbed himself instead.}ale rozmyslel se a bodl místo toho sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.52,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{The kid stabbed him!}Ten kluk ho bodl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.04,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{The piece of glass he used was there!}Střepy, které použil tam byly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.95,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There were cuts on the\Nhand he used to hold it!}Na ruce, kterou držel, byly škrty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.08,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara, you're a journalist.}Kakiharo, jsi novinář.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.47,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Can you see the truth\N through those warped eyes?}Dokážeš vidět pravdu přes ty pokřivené oči?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.65,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{There's information that\N wasn't released to the public.}Tyhle informace nebyly zveřejněny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:36.15,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{What was thought to be the father's \Ndying message was found at the scene.}To, co bylo považováno za umírající zprávu otce byl nalezeno na místě činu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.64,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Doesn't look like that to me.}To mi tak nepřipadá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:44.51,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{My personal interpretation is that\Nhe was trying to tell his son to live.}Mým osobním výkladem je to, že se pokoušel říct svému synovi, aby žil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.58,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Live?}Žil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.93,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, right.}Jo, správně.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.93,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{It can't be.}To nemůže být.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.42,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{His son stabbed him.}Jeho syn ho bodl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.26,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, Kakihara...}Hej, Kakiharo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:11:01.23,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{It's easy to tell someone to die, \Nbut it's hard to tell them to live.}Je snadné někomu říct umři, ale mnohem těžší říct mu žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:06.43,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Especially for someone\N who's about to be killed.}Obzvlášť někomu koho ses chystal zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.56,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He didn't kill him?}On ho nezabil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.04,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{It's me.}To jsem já.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.88,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Got it. Tomorrow morning.}Mám to. Zítra ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.66,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{That was Kamina.}To byl Kamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.53,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{He wants us to gather at the church.}Chce, abychom se shromáždili u kostela.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.69,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I refuse. I refuse to accept this.}Odmítám. Odmítám to přijmout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.29,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara...}Kakiharo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.96,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He freed himself from the hands of\N the father who tried to die with him!}Osvobodil se z rukou otce, který se s ním snažil zemřít!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:37.04,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He refused to die with his father\N and killed him instead!}On odmítl umřít se svým otcem a místo toho ho zabil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:45.38,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{We know the Foundation is trying\N to cause a second Great Collapse.}Víme, že se nadace snaží způsobit druhé Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.81,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{A second Great Collapse?}Druhé Velké zhroucení?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.23,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's no good.}To není dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.35,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{To prepare for the Collapse,\N my father has transferred}Abyc se připravil na zhroucení, můj otec přenesl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.66,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{a number of large machines\N from the research lab.}z výzkumné laboratoře řadu velkých strojů.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.36,Shinsou main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{What kind of machines?}Jaký druh strojů?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.11,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not sure.}Nejsem si jista.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.64,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Where were they taken?}Kde je vzali?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.40,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know that, either. I'm sorry.}To nevím. Omlouvám.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.75,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{It's fine.}To je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.10,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Knowing the Foundation's plan\Nis more than enough.}Znalost plánu nadace je víc než dost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.41,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{If they cause another Great Collapse,\Nwe'll all be turned into monsters.}Pokud způsobí další Velké zhroucení, budeme všichni přeměněni na příšery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.29,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You've been deceived.}Byli jste oklamáni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:17.63,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're causing needless worry\N so we'll fall into your trap.}Budete působit zbytečné starosti, takže padneme do pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.05,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{N-No!}N-Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri's on our side now.}Yuri je teď na naší straně.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I trust her.}Věřím ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.37,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Me, too. She saved my life.}I já. Zachránila mi život.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.07,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's investigate immediately.}Okamžitě to prošetříme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.12,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You will regret this.}Budete toho litovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.27,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Everyone's so nice.}Všichni jsou tak milí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:39.77,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.99,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami-san and her friends\N are helping us now.}Kurokami a její přátelé nám teď pomáhají.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all thanks to you.}To všechno díky tobě.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.47,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's because you saved Kotetsu.}To protože jsi zachránila Kotetsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.14,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank you.}Děkuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.37,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I just...}Jen jsem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.24,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I just wanted to help you.}Jen jsem ti chtěla pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.62,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.11,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you bring it?}Přinesla jsi to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.65,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, but...}Jo, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.69,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I want to remember you.}Chci si na tebe pamatovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.30,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no rush. You can take your time.}Žádnej spěch. Vem jsi kolik času můžeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{My memories begin with despair.}Moje vzpomínky začínají zoufalstvím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:34.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{If I'm aiming for a new future,\N I want something to support that.}Pokud usiluju o novou budoucnost, chci něčím pomoci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You said it was my mother's fault.}Řekla jsi, že to byla matčina chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe you're right.}Možná máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But if everything began with my mom,}Ale všechno začalo s mou matkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:50.06,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{then maybe my mother's the\N reason we met and were reunited.}potom je má matka možná důvodem našeho potkání a shledání.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.89,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.37,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's okay.}To je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:59.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You gave me hope and the\N courage to face things head on.}Dala jsi mi naději a odvahu čelit věcem přímo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.04,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I didn't..}To ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:04.79,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{This is my chance to regain what I lost.}To je moje šance získat zpět to, co jsem ztratil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.95,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{My fate is beginning to change.}Můj osud se začíná měnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.56,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I know it is.}Já to vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.89,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{The Tempest,}{\i0} {\i1}{huh?}Bouře{\i0}, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.90,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Your mother gave it to me.}Tvá matka mi ho dala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.47,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{This came to mind first when\N I was looking for keepsakes.}To přišlo na mysl jako první, když jsem hledala dárek na památku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's my favorite book.}Je to má oblíbená knížka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.36,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Even though they reach\N the depths of despair,}I přesto, že se dostanou do hlubin zoufalství,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{in the end, they're all happy.}nakonec, jsou všichni šťastní.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:36.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{"As you from crimes would pardoned be,}"Jako bys ty zločiny omluvil,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Let your indulgence set me free."}nechť mě osvobodí tvé odpustky. "
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.58,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.29,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.26,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.57,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.53,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why won't you come home, Mitsuki?}Proč nepřijdeš domů, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.94,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why?}Proč, proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.54,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why won't you come home?}Proč nepřijdeš domů?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.02,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Have you abandoned me?}Opustila jsi mě?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.04,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why?}Proč, proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.76,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't abandon me.}Neopouštěj mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.70,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.13,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.60,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.48,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? Why?}Proč, proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.22,Shinsou main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,{Why did you kill your father?}Proč jsi zabil tvého otce?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.54,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I...}Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.62,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Recently, the AVAL Science Foundation}Nedávno byla založena vědecká nadace AVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.08,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{has forcibly acquired several\N properties within the city.}násilně získal několik nemovitostí uvnitř města.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.19,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Numerous vehicles are\Nentering and exiting them.}Mnoho vozidel vjíždí a vyjíždí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:42.38,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Are they transporting the machines\N Shiraki Yuri mentioned?}Převážejí zmíněné stroje Shiraki Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.04,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going inside to check things out.}Jdu dovnitř, abych to zkontrolovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.28,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Signing off.}Končím.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.10,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{This is awful.}To je hrozné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.72,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{This is...}To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.89,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{They're artificially creating barriers.}Uměle vytvářejí bariéry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:17.12,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{If these are at all the properties\N the Foundation acquired...}Pokud se jedná o všechny nemovitosti, které nadace získala ...
