Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:18.90,sign_23466_252_Show_On_Map,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{Show On Map}Ukázat na mapě
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.20,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{If I'm right, then...}Pokud mám pravdu, potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.43,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Who's there?!}Kdo je tam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.72,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Beautiful, isn't it?}Překrásné, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.19,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the ultimate requiem I offer up to you.}Je to konečná zádušní mše, kterou vám nabídnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.56,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you okay, Chihiro-kun?}Jsi v pořádku, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.77,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened?}Co se stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.66,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{You suddenly collapsed\N when you touched the book.}Najednou ses zhroutil, když ses dotkl knihy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.88,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you remember something?}Vzpomněl sis na něco?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.98,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No.}Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.25,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I see, that's too bad.}Vidím, že je to dost špatné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry.}Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, right!}No, jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.13,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I had another dream.}Měl jsem další sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.73,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,Pluto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.40,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I shall shatter the demon's night}Rozbiji démonovu noc
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.84,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{and illuminate the dark paths of the world.}a osvětluji temné cesty světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.30,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.81,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.53,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{You think you've won?}Myslíš, že jsi vyhrál?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.86,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{You underestimate my immortal familiar.}Podceňuješ mé nesmrtelné známé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.11,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,Pluto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:41.37,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death to the undying.}Nehynoucí smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.12,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Such is the reaper's scythe.}Taková je smrťákova kosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.29,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{This isn't over!}Tohle není konec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.36,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,Tokotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.19,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I shall sing your praises.}Budu zpívat tvé chvály.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.42,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death is kind to all.}Smrt je laskavá ke všem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.26,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't reach me from there.}Nemůžeš mě odtud dostat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.02,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death has arrived.}Smrt dorazila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.62,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Where's Kurokami-san?}Kde je Kurokami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.44,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't get a hold of her.}Nemůžeme se jí dovolat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.32,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{She got what she deserved.}Dostala, co si zasloužila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.97,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{She was deceived by the enemy's words.}Byla podvedena slovy nepřítele.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.41,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The Guardian State's not so special after all.}Vládní strážci nejsou nic speciálního potom všem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.73,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Shut up!}Sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.84,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Where is she?!}Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.17,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Did she say where she was investigating?!}Říkala, kde vyšetřuje?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.62,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't yell at me.}Nezírejte na mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.17,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I let you listen to the message she left.}Nechala jsem vás poslouchat vzkaz, který zanechala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.80,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If anything happened to her, it's your fault.}Pokud se jí něco stane, je to tvoje chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.20,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san?}Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.62,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.28,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Wake up!}Vstávej!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.43,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened? Kurokami!}Co se stalo? Kurokami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.67,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is...}To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.19,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You found something?}Tys něco našla?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.45,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.70,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:09.95,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:14.09,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{We're one step closer to the\Nfulfillment of Chaos' ambition.}Jsme o krok blíže k naplnění chaosových ambicí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.30,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Well done, Yuri-san.}Dobrá práce, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.78,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I didn't—}Já nic—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.90,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami-san believed your\Nwords and was defeated}Kurokami tvým slovům věřila a byla poražena
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.89,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{without realizing she'd been deceived.}aniž by si uvědomila, že byla oklamána.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.37,Shinsou main,CHIHIARO,0000,0000,0000,,{No! Yuri didn't do—}Ne! Yuri nic neudě—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.80,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Father.}Otče.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.07,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Well done, my beloved daughter.}Dobrá práce, má milovaná dcero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.60,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{It really was you.}Opravdu jsi to byla ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.75,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{No! I didn't!}Ne! Nebyla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.80,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You did your job.}Udělala jsi svou práci.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.04,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You can come home now, Yuri.}Můžeš jít domů Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri will never go back to you!}Yuri se k vám nikdy nevrátí!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:54.96,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri, you can only rest easy \Nat your father's side.}Yuri, můžeš v klidu po boku svého otce odpočívat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.65,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You know that.}Tys to věděla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.26,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You don't belong there anymore.}Už tam nepatříš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.90,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{They're here to take you home, Yuri-san.}Jsou tady, aby tě vzali domů, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.76,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait! There must be some mistake!}Počkejte! To musí být nějaká chyba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:10.33,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami said she wanted to trust you.}Kurokami řekla, že ti chtěla věřit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.77,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{She wanted to trust you.}Chtěla ti věřit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.95,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If you've got any excuses, let me hear them!}Pokud máš nějaké výmluvy, nech mě si je poslechnout!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I never deceived her. It's true!}Nikdy jsem ji podvedl. To je pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.40,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You have to believe me!}Musíte mi věřit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.15,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You say that}To říkáš {\i1}{now?}teď?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.68,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Marie was a good person.}Marie byla dobrý člověk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.39,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{A really good person.}Opravdu dobrý člověk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.19,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.48,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Come home, Yuri.}Pojď domů, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.67,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Please, guys.}Prosím, lidi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.25,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri is...}Yuri je...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.97,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.22,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:46.84,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.84,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't, Yuri!}Nedělej to, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:49.68,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.23,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait, Yuri!}Počkej, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.19,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Fool!}Blázne!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.93,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you think you could leave me?}Myslela sis, že mě můžeš opustit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.08,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Though we were able to kill\None of the Heroic Lineage,}I když jsme byli schopni zabít jednoho z hrdinské linie,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.92,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll never forgive you for betraying me!}Nikdy ti neodpustím, že jsi mě zradila!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.59,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Listen, Yuri.}Poslouchej, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.09,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{That place is important to Mitsuki and I.}To místo je důležité pro Mitsuki a mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.50,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You are never permitted there!}Nebude ti nikdy dovoleno tam být!
